{"tid":2495733,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港電台：科興疫苗於智利有效率67%","createTime":"2021-04-19T11:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T11:18:30.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"31dabf3e3a88b99660922f405e029d037eb86eb0","tid":2495733,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T11:02:38.000Z","msg":"香港電台力排眾議，大大聲話「科興有效率67%」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n智利公布一項在現實生活的大規模研究顯示，<strong>中國科興新冠疫苗對預防出現有症狀感染的有效率為67%。</strong><br />\n<br />\n當局根據2月和3月疫苗接種計劃的數據，比較接種1劑疫苗、完成兩劑接種與沒有注射疫苗人士的情況後得出結論，共涉及1050萬人。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，接種疫苗對預防有症狀感染的有效率為67%；對預防住院治療的有效率為85%；防止染疫後死亡的有效率為80%。<br />\n<br />\n智利至今已有760萬人打了至少一劑疫苗，其中500多萬人接種了兩劑，佔目標人口的三分一。<br />\n<br />\n智利取得的疫苗中，86.7%屬科興疫苗，其餘為輝瑞/BioNtech疫苗。根據協議，智利將分三年購買6千萬劑科興疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586308-20210417.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586308-20210417.htm&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqxzYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=3bc8c759\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586308-20210417.htm&h=77aa0a6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586308-20210417.htm</a>"},{"pid":"fcca181a2b7387889d50abaa3d2efb9defe3557e","tid":2495733,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T11:04:27.000Z","msg":"智利呢D垃圾國應該都係收皮"},{"pid":"d13fb89354c202115bf2dd14a2d07554420d9e0b","tid":2495733,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T11:05:12.000Z","msg":"有效感染率<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e12d12b93a5c0f6c1bd934e97b648e56ec276bd","tid":2495733,"uid":192813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T11:05:17.000Z","msg":"香港電台都變咗cctv <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc5d511444958749dccafe75a1ba52a2e2c7c2c","tid":2495733,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T11:15:20.000Z","msg":"碌柒"},{"pid":"213b7fe7a204ecdf357f821b0d1da7c27aa0bf5e","tid":2495733,"uid":157793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T11:18:30.000Z","msg":"死亡效率有67%"}]}